        context_item("Lesson Synthesis", "“Today we created our own class number line and analyzed number lines. What do we need to think about when\ncreating a number line to represent numbers?” (We should use the same amount of space between each tick mark. We\nshould make sure labels on tick marks show the right length from 0 and are the right length from each other. We should\nmake sure the number labels are in the correct order. We can think about a ruler to check if the number line makes\nsense.)", line(318))
