        context_item("Warm-up — Activity Synthesis", "• “What pattern do you see as you look at the\n\nexpressions and their values? Why is that\n\nhappening?” (Each of the first addends has a 9 in the\n\nones place. You can make a ten for each expression.\nThe number in the ones place of the value of each\nexpression is 1 less than the second addend. This is\nbecause you can take 1 from each addend to make a\nten with the first addend.)\n• As needed, record students’ thinking, using a number\nline or base-ten diagram.\n• Consider asking:\n◦ “Did anyone notice a different pattern”?\n◦ “Did anyone notice the same pattern but would\nexplain it differently?”", line(106)),
