        context_item("Activity 1 — Student Task Statement", "1. Use the materials to design your own game.\n\na. What are the rules of your game?\n\nb. How does someone win the game?\n\n2. Test out your game at least 1 time.\n3. Redesign your game to include at least 2 of the\nfollowing:\n◦ length or distance measurement in inches\n\n◦ time that has passed\n◦ multiplication or division within 100\n\n◦ addition or subtraction within 1,000\n\nIf you have time, play the new and improved game.", line(201))
