        context_item("Activity 1 — Student Task Statement", "Students are preparing for a\nparty. The school has tables\nwhere 6 people can sit and\ntables where 8 people can\nsit.\n\nThe students can only\nchoose one type of table\nand they want to avoid\n\nhaving empty seats.\n\n1. Jada’s class has 18 students. Which table would\nyou choose for Jada’s class? Explain or show\nyour reasoning.\n2. Noah’s class has 30 students. Which table\nwould you choose for Noah’s class? Explain or\nshow your reasoning.\n3. Which table would you choose for Noah’s and\nJada’s classes together? Can you find more\nthan one option? Explain or show your\nreasoning.\n\n4. If you also want places for Noah’s teacher and\nJada’s teacher to sit, which table would you\nchoose? Explain or show your reasoning.", line(174)),
