        context_item("Cool-down — Student Task Statement", "Complete the statements for each number.\n\nnumber                                factor                                                  multiple\n\n11              ______ is a factor of ______ because . . .              ______ is a multiple of ______ because . . .\n\n24              ______ is a factor of ______ because . . .              ______ is a multiple of ______ because . . .", line(397))
