        context_item("Cool-down — Student Task Statement", "1.    a. Which two multiples of 10,000 are closest to 627,800?\nb. Of the two multiples of 10,000, which one is closer to 627,800?\n\n2.    a. Which two multiples of 100,000 are closest to 627,800?\nb. Of the two multiples of 100,000 which one is closer to 627,800?", line(389))
