        context_item("Activity 1 — Student Task Statement", "Your teacher will give you a fact sheet about some\nanimals or ask you to perform some research.\n1. Choose 2 animals that you would like to\ncompare.\n\n2. Use the information from your teacher or your\nresearch to write 2 true comparison\nstatements and 1 false comparison statement\nabout these animals.\n\na. Write 1 statement on the front side of each\n\nindex card.\n\nb. On the back side of each card, write\nwhether the statement is true or false.", line(172)),
        context_item("Activity 2 — Student Task Statement", "1. Read at least 5 statements that are not yours\nand decide if they are true.\n◦ Find at least one statement that is false.\nWrite down the statement here. Explain or\n\nshow how you know.\n◦ If a statement you read is unclear, use a\nsticky note to leave a comment or question\nfor the writer.\n2. Collect your cards and any notes that your\nclassmates might have left for you.\n\n◦ Think about how to make revisions to\nmake your statements stronger and               A\nclearer.\n\n◦ Record your revised statements here.", line(241))
