        context_item("Cool-down — Student Task Statement", "1. Circle the statement and the multiplication equation that show a comparison of Tyler’s and Elena’s cubes.\n\nTyler has 4 more cubes than Elena.\n\nElena has 5 times as many cubes as Tyler.\n\nTyler has 5 times as many cubes as Elena.\n\nTyler has 4 times as many cubes as Elena.\n\n2. Explain your choices.", line(369))
