        context_item("Cool-down — Student Task Statement", "Kiran created a number pattern that follows the rule “start with 0, keep adding 8.”\nkeep adding 8           1. Complete the table to show the first 6 numbers in Kiran’s pattern.\n\n0                  2. Could 105 be a number that Kiran writes if he continued his pattern? Explain or\nshow your reasoning.", line(391))
