        context_item("Activity 1 — Student Task Statement", "1. In each case, draw a horizontal line and\nmeasure the angle that the street makes when\nit meets the horizontal line.\na.\n\nb.\n\nc.\n\nd.\n\ne.\n\n2. How is living on a steep street different from\nliving on a level or flat street? Think of as many\ndifferences as you can.", line(158)),
