        context_item("Lesson Synthesis", "“Today we used what we’ve learned about measuring angles to solve some problems about streets at different angles\nand how the number and steepness of steps depends on the angle.”\n\n“What were some decisions that you needed to make as you drew the steps that were at different angles? How did the\ndecisions affect the solutions to the problems?” (We had to decide how far the parking lot was from the playground\nwhich affected how many steps we would need. We had to decide when the steps were too steep to climb. We decided\nthat if the steps were taller than they were long, then they were too steep, which was at around   .)\n\nConsider having students respond to the previous question as a journal prompt.", line(373))
