        context_item("Lesson Synthesis", "“Today we analyzed and solved many kinds of word problems.“\n\n“What are some strategies we should use when solving problems to make sure we understand what the problem is\nasking?” (Read it carefully, think about what the numbers tell us and how they are related to each other.)\n\n“What are some ways to figure out the relationships between the numbers?” (Create a representation—an equation or a\ndiagram—and check to see if the representation matches the problem being solved.)\n\n“How would we know if our answer makes sense?” (Check to see if it’s reasonable in the situation, double check our\ncalculations, check to see if it answers the question.)", line(288))
