        context_item("Warm-up — Activity Synthesis", "• “What are some things we have to think about if we\nplan a book fair for our school?” (The different types\n\nof books we sell and have to order, the cost of the\nbooks for us, the amount to charge for each book,\nthe number of people who come to the fair, and the\n\nnumber of books that we sell.)", line(98)),
