        context_item("Activity 2 — Student Task Statement", "Recall that Diego threw a disc 5.1 meters, and Jada\nthrew it 5.01 meters. For each question, find 2\npossible answers.\n\n1. Han threw the disc farther than Diego. How far\nmight Han have thrown the disc?\n2. Tyler threw the disc farther than Diego but less\nthan 6 meters. How far might Tyler have\n\nthrown the disc?\n3. Mai threw the disc a shorter distance than\nJada. How far might Mai have thrown the disc?\n4. Priya threw the disc a shorter distance than\nJada but more than 5 meters. How far might\nPriya have thrown the disc?", line(222)),
