        context_item("Warm-up — Activity Synthesis", "• “Is the statement              true or false? How do\nyou know?” (False, because 0.909 has 9 tenths and 9\nthousandths and 0.91 is 9 tenths and 1 hundredth. 1\nhundredth is greater than 9 thousandths.)\n• Display: 0.909 and 0.910\n• “How does writing the numbers like this help to\ncompare them?” (I can see that 0.910 has 10\nthousandths compared to 9 for 0.909.)", line(92)),
