        context_item("Activity 1 — Student Task Statement", "Use the directions to play Greatest Sum with a\npartner.\n\n1. Spin the spinner.\n\n2. Write the number in an empty box for Round\n1. Be sure your partner can’t see your paper.\nOnce a number is written down, it can’t be\nchanged.\n\n3. Take turns. Spin and write numbers in the\n\nempty boxes until all 4 boxes have been filled.\n\n4. Find the sum.\n\n5. The partner with the greater sum wins the\n\nround.\n\n6. The partner who won the most rounds wins\nthe game. If there is a tie, players add the sums\nfrom all 4 rounds. The greater total sum wins\nthe game.\n\nRound 1\n\nRound 2\n\nRound 3\n\nRound 4\n\nTotal sum of all 4 rounds:", line(151)),
