        context_item("Activity 1 — Activity Synthesis", "• Display 4 circles.\n• “I need to draw a group of things that has more than\nthis group.”\n• Draw 2 circles.\n• “Does this group have more things? How can you\ntell?” (No, I know 2 is less than 4.)\n• Draw 2 more circles.\n• “Does this group have more things? How can you\ntell?” (No, they both have 4 circles, so they are the\nsame.)\n• Draw 1 more circle.\n• “Does this group have more things? How can you\ntell?” (Yes, because they both have 4, but your group\nhas 1 more.)\n• “What if I drew another circle?” (You would still have\nmore. You could keep drawing as many circles as you\nwant and you will always have more than 4.)", line(205)),
