        context_item("Activity 1 — Activity Synthesis", "• “How did you know how many plants to put in your\ngarden?” (We saw the number 4 and put 4 plants in\nour garden.)\n• Display the number 7.\n• “I’m going to put the plants in the garden. Tell me\nwhen I should stop putting plants in the garden.”\n• Count as you put each counter in the garden. Do not\nstop adding counters until the class tells you to.\n• If the class tells you to stop after placing 7 counters,\nask:\n◦ “Why do I need to stop putting plants in the\ngarden?”\n◦ “How many plants are in the garden? How do\nyou know?”\n• If the class does not tell you to stop placing the\ncounters, place 10‒15 counters on the garden and\nask:\n◦ “How many plants are in the garden now? How\nmany plants was I supposed to put in my\ngarden?”", line(191)),
