        context_item("Activity 1 — Activity Synthesis", "• Display the number 6 and three different cube\ntowers (2, 6, and 10).\n• “Which tower matches this number? How do you\nknow?” (6, I counted and there were 6 cubes. I can\ntell by looking that this one only has 2 cubes and the\nbig one has too many cubes to be 6.)", line(181)),
