        context_item("Lesson Synthesis", "“How did you choose to show how you would pack the fruit in the box? Did you use objects or draw a picture or do\nsomething else?” (I used connecting cubes. I drew a picture.)\n\n“If you used objects, how did the objects help you show how you would pack the box?” (I used objects, because I could\nshow the bananas using yellow connecting cubes and the apples using green connecting cubes.)\n\n“If you drew a picture, how did drawing a picture help you show how you would pack the box?” (I drew a picture, so I\ncould draw each fruit and write how many of each fruit would be in the box.)\n\n“If you did something else, how did it help you show how you would pack the box?”\n\nKindergarten                                    CC BY NC 2024", line(228))
